{
  "video_id": "WwB6bPgPol4",
  "title": "Witness: Illuminating the World of Modern-day Slavery: Lisa Kristine at TEDxMaui",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13432.0,
      "end_time": 20003.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m 150 feet down an illegal mine shaft in Ghana."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20003.0,
      "end_time": 24474.0,
      "text": "The air is thick with heat and dust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 24474.0,
      "end_time": 27513.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s hard to breathe."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 27513.0,
      "end_time": 31534.0,
      "text": "I can feel the brush of sweaty bodies passing me in the darkness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 31534.0,
      "end_time": 34925.0,
      "text": "but I can&#39;t see much else."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 34925.0,
      "end_time": 38258.0,
      "text": "I hear voices talking, but mostly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 38258.0,
      "end_time": 42680.0,
      "text": "the shaft is this cacophony of men coughing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 42680.0,
      "end_time": 47350.0,
      "text": "and stone being broken with primitive tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 47350.0,
      "end_time": 51128.0,
      "text": "Like the others, I wear a flickering, cheap flashlight"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 51128.0,
      "end_time": 55196.0,
      "text": "tied to my head with this elastic, tattered band,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 55196.0,
      "end_time": 58824.0,
      "text": "and I can barely make out the slick tree limbs"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 58824.0,
      "end_time": 62243.0,
      "text": "holding up the walls of the three-foot square hole"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 62243.0,
      "end_time": 66544.0,
      "text": "dropping hundreds of feet into the earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 66544.0,
      "end_time": 69047.0,
      "text": "When my hand slips, I suddenly remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 69047.0,
      "end_time": 72059.0,
      "text": "a miner I had met days before"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 72059.0,
      "end_time": 76265.0,
      "text": "who had lost his grip and fell countless feet"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 76265.0,
      "end_time": 78591.0,
      "text": "down that shaft."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78591.0,
      "end_time": 81157.0,
      "text": "As I stand talking to you today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 81157.0,
      "end_time": 84576.0,
      "text": "these men are still deep in that hole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 84576.0,
      "end_time": 88293.0,
      "text": "risking their lives without payment or compensation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 88293.0,
      "end_time": 92067.0,
      "text": "and often dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 92067.0,
      "end_time": 94767.0,
      "text": "I got to climb out of that hole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 94767.0,
      "end_time": 97577.0,
      "text": "and I got to go home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 97577.0,
      "end_time": 103810.0,
      "text": "but they likely never will, because they&#39;re trapped in slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 103810.0,
      "end_time": 107321.0,
      "text": "For the last 28 years, I&#39;ve been documenting indigenous cultures"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 107321.0,
      "end_time": 110426.0,
      "text": "in more than 70 countries on six continents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 110426.0,
      "end_time": 113516.0,
      "text": "and in 2009 I had the great honor"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 113516.0,
      "end_time": 117148.0,
      "text": "of being the sole exhibitor at the Vancouver Peace Summit."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 117148.0,
      "end_time": 120639.0,
      "text": "Amongst all the astonishing people I met there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 120639.0,
      "end_time": 124337.0,
      "text": "I met a supporter of Free the Slaves, an NGO"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 124337.0,
      "end_time": 129221.0,
      "text": "dedicated to eradicating modern day slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 129221.0,
      "end_time": 132157.0,
      "text": "We started talking about slavery, and really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 132157.0,
      "end_time": 134876.0,
      "text": "I started learning about slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 134876.0,
      "end_time": 138243.0,
      "text": "for I had certainly known it existed in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 138243.0,
      "end_time": 141252.0,
      "text": "but not to such a degree."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 141252.0,
      "end_time": 144924.0,
      "text": "After we finished talking, I felt so horrible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 144924.0,
      "end_time": 148274.0,
      "text": "and honestly ashamed at my own lack of knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 148274.0,
      "end_time": 151379.0,
      "text": "of this atrocity in my own lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 151379.0,
      "end_time": 153423.0,
      "text": "And I thought, if I don&#39;t know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 153423.0,
      "end_time": 157143.0,
      "text": "how many other people don&#39;t know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 157143.0,
      "end_time": 160786.0,
      "text": "It started burning a hole in my stomach, so within weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 160786.0,
      "end_time": 164514.0,
      "text": "I flew down to Los Angeles to meet with the director of Free the Slaves"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 164514.0,
      "end_time": 166961.0,
      "text": "and offer them my help."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 166961.0,
      "end_time": 171414.0,
      "text": "Thus began my journey into modern day slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 171414.0,
      "end_time": 175023.0,
      "text": "Oddly, I had been to many of these places before."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 175023.0,
      "end_time": 178191.0,
      "text": "Some I even considered like my second home."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 178191.0,
      "end_time": 180004.0,
      "text": "But this time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 180004.0,
      "end_time": 185367.0,
      "text": "I would see the skeletons hidden in the closet."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 185367.0,
      "end_time": 187960.0,
      "text": "A conservative estimate tells us"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 187960.0,
      "end_time": 193244.0,
      "text": "there are more than 27 million people enslaved in the world today."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 193244.0,
      "end_time": 196492.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s double the amount of people taken from Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 196492.0,
      "end_time": 200720.0,
      "text": "during the entire trans-Atlantic slave trade."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 200720.0,
      "end_time": 202464.0,
      "text": "A hundred and fifty years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 202464.0,
      "end_time": 209901.0,
      "text": "an agricultural slave cost about 3 times the annual salary of an American worker."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 209901.0,
      "end_time": 214065.0,
      "text": "That equates to about $50,000 in today&#39;s money."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 214065.0,
      "end_time": 219256.0,
      "text": "Yet today, entire families can be enslaved for generations"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 219256.0,
      "end_time": 224476.0,
      "text": "over a debt as small as $18."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 224476.0,
      "end_time": 227724.0,
      "text": "Astonishingly, slavery generates profits"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 227724.0,
      "end_time": 234937.0,
      "text": "of more than $13 billion worldwide each year."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 234937.0,
      "end_time": 238834.0,
      "text": "Many have been tricked by false promises"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 238834.0,
      "end_time": 242007.0,
      "text": "of a good education, a better job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 242007.0,
      "end_time": 244793.0,
      "text": "only to find that they&#39;re forced to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 244793.0,
      "end_time": 247759.0,
      "text": "without pay, under the threat of violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 247759.0,
      "end_time": 252425.0,
      "text": "and they cannot walk away."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 252425.0,
      "end_time": 254891.0,
      "text": "Today&#39;s slavery is about commerce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 254891.0,
      "end_time": 259230.0,
      "text": "so the goods that enslaved people produce have value,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 259230.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264177.0,
      "text": "but the people producing them are disposable."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 264177.0,
      "end_time": 268184.0,
      "text": "Slavery exists everywhere, nearly, in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 268184.0,
      "end_time": 276190.0,
      "text": "and yet it is illegal everywhere in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 276190.0,
      "end_time": 280246.0,
      "text": "In India and Nepal, I was introduced to the brick kilns."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 280246.0,
      "end_time": 282714.0,
      "text": "This strange and awesome sight"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 282714.0,
      "end_time": 286772.0,
      "text": "was like walking into ancient Egypt or Dante&#39;s Inferno."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 286772.0,
      "end_time": 291284.0,
      "text": "Enveloped in temperatures of 130 degrees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 291284.0,
      "end_time": 295331.0,
      "text": "men, women, children, entire families in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 295331.0,
      "end_time": 298428.0,
      "text": "were cloaked in a heavy blanket of dust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 298428.0,
      "end_time": 303222.0,
      "text": "while mechanically stacking bricks on their head, up to 18 at a time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 303222.0,
      "end_time": 306269.0,
      "text": "and carrying them from the scorching kilns"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 306269.0,
      "end_time": 309249.0,
      "text": "to trucks hundreds of yards away."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 309249.0,
      "end_time": 312712.0,
      "text": "Deadened by monotony and exhaustion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 312712.0,
      "end_time": 314847.0,
      "text": "they work silently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 314847.0,
      "end_time": 318358.0,
      "text": "doing this task over and over"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 318358.0,
      "end_time": 321526.0,
      "text": "for 16 or 17 hours a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 321526.0,
      "end_time": 325120.0,
      "text": "There were no breaks for food, no water breaks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 325120.0,
      "end_time": 330379.0,
      "text": "and the severe dehydration made urinating pretty much inconsequential."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 330379.0,
      "end_time": 333508.0,
      "text": "So pervasive was the heat and the dust"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 333508.0,
      "end_time": 338982.0,
      "text": "that my camera became too hot to even touch and ceased working."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 338982.0,
      "end_time": 341889.0,
      "text": "Every 20 minutes, I&#39;d have to run back to our cruiser"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 341889.0,
      "end_time": 347046.0,
      "text": "to clean out my gear and run it under an air conditioner to revive it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 347046.0,
      "end_time": 348984.0,
      "text": "and as I sat there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 348984.0,
      "end_time": 350667.0,
      "text": "I thought, my camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 350667.0,
      "end_time": 357455.0,
      "text": "is getting far better treatment than these people."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 357455.0,
      "end_time": 361052.0,
      "text": "Back in the kilns, I wanted to cry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 361052.0,
      "end_time": 364054.0,
      "text": "but the abolitionist next to me quickly grabbed me and he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 364054.0,
      "end_time": 367886.0,
      "text": "&quot;Lisa, don&#39;t do that. Just don&#39;t do that here.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 367886.0,
      "end_time": 370237.0,
      "text": "And he very clearly explained to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 370237.0,
      "end_time": 374188.0,
      "text": "that emotional displays are very dangerous in a place like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 374188.0,
      "end_time": 378929.0,
      "text": "not just for me, but for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 378929.0,
      "end_time": 381701.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t offer them any direct help."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 381701.0,
      "end_time": 384628.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t give them money, nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 384628.0,
      "end_time": 386538.0,
      "text": "I wasn&#39;t a citizen of that country."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 386538.0,
      "end_time": 392245.0,
      "text": "I could get them in a worse situation than they were already in."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 392245.0,
      "end_time": 394255.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d have to rely on Free the Slaves"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 394255.0,
      "end_time": 397291.0,
      "text": "to work within the system for their liberation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 397291.0,
      "end_time": 400822.0,
      "text": "and I trusted that they would."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 400822.0,
      "end_time": 402577.0,
      "text": "As for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 402577.0,
      "end_time": 404408.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d have to wait until I got home"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 404408.0,
      "end_time": 409784.0,
      "text": "to really feel my heartbreak."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 409784.0,
      "end_time": 412464.0,
      "text": "In the Himalayas, I found children carrying stone"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 412464.0,
      "end_time": 415264.0,
      "text": "for miles down mountainous terrain"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 415264.0,
      "end_time": 418950.0,
      "text": "to trucks waiting at roads below."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 418950.0,
      "end_time": 422188.0,
      "text": "The big sheets of slate were heavier"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 422188.0,
      "end_time": 424306.0,
      "text": "than the children carrying them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 424306.0,
      "end_time": 426334.0,
      "text": "and the kids hoisted them from their heads"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 426334.0,
      "end_time": 429175.0,
      "text": "using these handmade harnesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 429175.0,
      "end_time": 432995.0,
      "text": "of sticks and rope and torn cloth."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 432995.0,
      "end_time": 436981.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s difficult to witness something so overwhelming."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 436981.0,
      "end_time": 440145.0,
      "text": "How can we affect something so insidious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 440145.0,
      "end_time": 443432.0,
      "text": "yet so pervasive?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 443432.0,
      "end_time": 445740.0,
      "text": "Some don&#39;t even know they&#39;re enslaved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 445740.0,
      "end_time": 449903.0,
      "text": "people working 16, 17 hours a day"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 449903.0,
      "end_time": 451596.0,
      "text": "without any pay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 451596.0,
      "end_time": 454700.0,
      "text": "because this has been the case all their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 454700.0,
      "end_time": 458733.0,
      "text": "They have nothing to compare it to."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 458733.0,
      "end_time": 462687.0,
      "text": "When these villagers claimed their freedom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 462687.0,
      "end_time": 467753.0,
      "text": "the slaveholders burned down all of their houses."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 467753.0,
      "end_time": 469786.0,
      "text": "I mean, these people had nothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 469786.0,
      "end_time": 473575.0,
      "text": "and they were so petrified, they wanted to give up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 473575.0,
      "end_time": 477503.0,
      "text": "but the woman in the center rallied for them to persevere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 477503.0,
      "end_time": 481574.0,
      "text": "and abolitionists on the ground helped them get a quarry lease of their own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 481574.0,
      "end_time": 485009.0,
      "text": "so that now they do the same back-breaking work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 485009.0,
      "end_time": 489242.0,
      "text": "but they do it for themselves, and they get paid for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 489242.0,
      "end_time": 495036.0,
      "text": "and they do it in freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 495036.0,
      "end_time": 499032.0,
      "text": "Sex trafficking is what we often think of when we hear the word slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 499032.0,
      "end_time": 501124.0,
      "text": "and because of this worldwide awareness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 501124.0,
      "end_time": 503774.0,
      "text": "I was warned that it would be difficult for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 503774.0,
      "end_time": 507546.0,
      "text": "to work safely within this particular industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 507546.0,
      "end_time": 509923.0,
      "text": "In Kathmandu, I was escorted by women"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 509923.0,
      "end_time": 513881.0,
      "text": "who had previously been sex slaves themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 513881.0,
      "end_time": 516008.0,
      "text": "They ushered me down a narrow set of stairs"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 516008.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521726.00000000006,
      "text": "that led to this dirty, dimly fluorescent lit basement."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 521726.0,
      "end_time": 523448.0,
      "text": "This wasn&#39;t a brothel, per se."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 523448.0,
      "end_time": 526774.0,
      "text": "It was more like a restaurant."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 526774.0,
      "end_time": 529200.0,
      "text": "Cabin restaurants, as they&#39;re known in the trade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 529200.0,
      "end_time": 531866.0,
      "text": "are venues for forced prostitution."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 531866.0,
      "end_time": 534006.0,
      "text": "Each has small, private rooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 534006.0,
      "end_time": 537393.0,
      "text": "where the slaves, women, along with young girls and boys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 537393.0,
      "end_time": 540164.0,
      "text": "some as young as seven years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 540164.0,
      "end_time": 542034.0,
      "text": "are forced to entertain the clients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 542034.0,
      "end_time": 546086.0,
      "text": "encouraging them to buy more food and alcohol."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 546086.0,
      "end_time": 549668.0,
      "text": "Each cubicle is dark and dingy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 549668.0,
      "end_time": 552839.0,
      "text": "identified with a painted number on the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 552839.0,
      "end_time": 556628.0,
      "text": "and partitioned by plywood and a curtain."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 556628.0,
      "end_time": 560400.0,
      "text": "The workers here often endure tragic sexual abuse"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 560400.0,
      "end_time": 563949.0,
      "text": "at the hands of their customers."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 563949.0,
      "end_time": 571005.0,
      "text": "Standing in the near darkness, I remember feeling this quick, hot fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 571005.0,
      "end_time": 573312.0,
      "text": "and in that instant, I could only imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 573312.0,
      "end_time": 577074.0,
      "text": "what it must be like to be trapped in that hell."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 577074.0,
      "end_time": 581395.0,
      "text": "I had only one way out: the stairs from where I&#39;d come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 581395.0,
      "end_time": 583118.0,
      "text": "There were no back doors."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 583118.0,
      "end_time": 585984.0,
      "text": "There were no windows large enough to climb through."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 585984.0,
      "end_time": 590312.0,
      "text": "These people have no escape at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 590312.0,
      "end_time": 593125.0,
      "text": "and as we take in such a difficult subject,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 593125.0,
      "end_time": 597539.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s important to note that slavery, including sex trafficking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 597539.0,
      "end_time": 600803.0,
      "text": "occurs in our own backyard as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 600803.0,
      "end_time": 605262.0,
      "text": "Tens of hundreds of people are enslaved in agriculture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 605262.0,
      "end_time": 608143.0,
      "text": "in restaurants, in domestic servitude,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 608143.0,
      "end_time": 610616.0,
      "text": "and the list can go on."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 610616.0,
      "end_time": 612923.0,
      "text": "Recently, the New York Times reported"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 612923.0,
      "end_time": 619167.0,
      "text": "that between 100,000 and 300,000 American children"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 619167.0,
      "end_time": 623007.0,
      "text": "are sold into sex slavery every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 623007.0,
      "end_time": 625403.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s all around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 625403.0,
      "end_time": 629759.0,
      "text": "We just don&#39;t see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 629759.0,
      "end_time": 633135.0,
      "text": "The textile industry is another one we often think of"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 633135.0,
      "end_time": 636566.0,
      "text": "when we hear about slave labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 636566.0,
      "end_time": 639849.0,
      "text": "I visited villages in India where entire families"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 639849.0,
      "end_time": 643258.0,
      "text": "were enslaved in the silk trade."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 643258.0,
      "end_time": 645480.0,
      "text": "This is a family portrait."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 645480.0,
      "end_time": 648737.0,
      "text": "The dyed black hands are the father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 648737.0,
      "end_time": 652244.0,
      "text": "while the blue and red hands are his sons."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 652244.0,
      "end_time": 654882.0,
      "text": "They mix dye in these big barrels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 654882.0,
      "end_time": 658831.0,
      "text": "and they submerge the silk into the liquid up to their elbows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 658831.0,
      "end_time": 663850.0,
      "text": "but the dye is toxic."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 663850.0,
      "end_time": 667193.0,
      "text": "My interpreter told me their stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 667193.0,
      "end_time": 671081.0,
      "text": "&quot;We have no freedom,&quot; they said."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 671081.0,
      "end_time": 674282.0,
      "text": "&quot;We hope still, though, that we could leave this house someday"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 674282.0,
      "end_time": 683057.0,
      "text": "and go someplace else where we actually get paid for our dyeing.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 683057.0,
      "end_time": 687170.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s estimated that more than 4,000 children"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 687170.0,
      "end_time": 689207.0,
      "text": "are enslaved on Lake Volta,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 689207.0,
      "end_time": 693281.0,
      "text": "the largest man-made lake in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 693281.0,
      "end_time": 696246.0,
      "text": "When we first arrived, I went to have a quick look."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 696246.0,
      "end_time": 700150.0,
      "text": "I saw what seemed to be a family fishing on a boat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 700150.0,
      "end_time": 704308.0,
      "text": "two older brothers, some younger kids, makes sense right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 704308.0,
      "end_time": 707962.0,
      "text": "Wrong. They were all enslaved."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 707962.0,
      "end_time": 710737.0,
      "text": "Children are taken from their families"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 710737.0,
      "end_time": 713143.0,
      "text": "and trafficked and vanished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 713143.0,
      "end_time": 717211.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re forced to work endless hours on these boats on the lake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 717211.0,
      "end_time": 722495.0,
      "text": "even though they do not know how to swim."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 722495.0,
      "end_time": 725295.0,
      "text": "This young child is 8 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 725295.0,
      "end_time": 727734.0,
      "text": "He was trembling when our boat approached,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 727734.0,
      "end_time": 731822.0,
      "text": "frightened it would run over his tiny canoe."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 731822.0,
      "end_time": 737110.0,
      "text": "He was petrified he would be knocked in the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 737110.0,
      "end_time": 740953.0,
      "text": "The skeletal tree limbs submerged in Lake Volta"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 740953.0,
      "end_time": 743570.0,
      "text": "often catch the fishing nets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 743570.0,
      "end_time": 747771.0,
      "text": "and weary, frightened children are thrown into the water"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 747771.0,
      "end_time": 750440.0,
      "text": "to untether the lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 750440.0,
      "end_time": 752269.0,
      "text": "Many of them drown."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 752269.0,
      "end_time": 755114.0,
      "text": "In fact, I didn&#39;t meet one child, not one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 755114.0,
      "end_time": 761684.0,
      "text": "who didn&#39;t know another who hadn&#39;t drown."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 761684.0,
      "end_time": 763599.0,
      "text": "For as long as he can recall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 763599.0,
      "end_time": 767351.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s been forced to work on the lake."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 767351.0,
      "end_time": 770851.0,
      "text": "Terrified of his master, he will not run away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 770851.0,
      "end_time": 774580.0,
      "text": "and since he&#39;s been treated with cruelty all his life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 774580.0,
      "end_time": 779817.0,
      "text": "he passes that down to the younger slaves that he manages."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 779817.0,
      "end_time": 781857.0,
      "text": "I met these boys at five in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 781857.0,
      "end_time": 785085.0,
      "text": "when they were hauling in the last of their nets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 785085.0,
      "end_time": 791038.0,
      "text": "but they had been working since 1 a.m. in the cold, windy night."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 791038.0,
      "end_time": 793708.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s important to note that these nets"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 793708.0,
      "end_time": 802235.0,
      "text": "weigh more than 1000 pounds when they&#39;re full of fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 802235.0,
      "end_time": 805858.0,
      "text": "I want to introduce you to Kofi."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 805858.0,
      "end_time": 809217.0,
      "text": "Kofi was rescued from a fishing village."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 809217.0,
      "end_time": 811935.0,
      "text": "I met him at a shelter  where Free the Slaves"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 811935.0,
      "end_time": 815629.0,
      "text": "rehabilitates victims of slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 815629.0,
      "end_time": 817636.0,
      "text": "Here he&#39;s seen taking a bath at the well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 817636.0,
      "end_time": 820413.0,
      "text": "pouring big buckets of water over his head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 820413.0,
      "end_time": 822349.0,
      "text": "and the wonderful news is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 822349.0,
      "end_time": 824712.0,
      "text": "as you and I are sitting here talking today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 824712.0,
      "end_time": 827639.0,
      "text": "Kofi has been reunited with his family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 827639.0,
      "end_time": 829245.0,
      "text": "and what&#39;s even better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 829245.0,
      "end_time": 832936.0,
      "text": "his family has been given tools to make a living"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 832936.0,
      "end_time": 836745.0,
      "text": "and to keep their children safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 836745.0,
      "end_time": 841195.0,
      "text": "Kofi is the embodiment of possibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 841195.0,
      "end_time": 845508.0,
      "text": "Who will he become because someone took a stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 845508.0,
      "end_time": 851040.0,
      "text": "and made a difference in his life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 851040.0,
      "end_time": 855291.0,
      "text": "Driving down a road in Ghana with partners of Free the Slaves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 855291.0,
      "end_time": 859392.0,
      "text": "a fellow abolitionist on a moped suddenly sped up to our cruiser"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 859392.0,
      "end_time": 861432.0,
      "text": "and tapped on the window."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 861432.0,
      "end_time": 866326.0,
      "text": "He told us to follow him down a dirt road into the jungle."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 866326.0,
      "end_time": 868861.0,
      "text": "At the end of the road, he urged us out of the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 868861.0,
      "end_time": 872226.0,
      "text": "and told the driver to quickly leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 872226.0,
      "end_time": 875430.0,
      "text": "Then he pointed toward this barely visible footpath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 875430.0,
      "end_time": 879726.0,
      "text": "and he said, &quot;This is the path, this is the path. Go.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 879726.0,
      "end_time": 881777.0,
      "text": "As we started down the path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 881777.0,
      "end_time": 884292.0,
      "text": "we pushed aside the vines blocking the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 884292.0,
      "end_time": 887179.0,
      "text": "and after about an hour of walking in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 887179.0,
      "end_time": 892454.0,
      "text": "found that the trail had become flooded by recent rains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 892454.0,
      "end_time": 894910.0,
      "text": "so I hoisted the photo gear above my head"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 894910.0,
      "end_time": 898936.0,
      "text": "as we descended into these waters up to my chest."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 898936.0,
      "end_time": 901690.0,
      "text": "After another two hours of hiking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 901690.0,
      "end_time": 905594.0,
      "text": "the winding trail abruptly ended at a clearing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 905594.0,
      "end_time": 908850.0,
      "text": "and before us was a mass of holes"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 908850.0,
      "end_time": 912703.0,
      "text": "that could fit into the size of a football field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 912703.0,
      "end_time": 919057.0,
      "text": "and all of them were full of enslaved people laboring."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 919057.0,
      "end_time": 921998.0,
      "text": "Many women had children strapped to their backs"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 921998.0,
      "end_time": 923834.0,
      "text": "while they were panning for gold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 923834.0,
      "end_time": 928806.0,
      "text": "wading in water poisoned by mercury."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 928806.0,
      "end_time": 936417.0,
      "text": "Mercury is used in the extraction process."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 936417.0,
      "end_time": 939795.0,
      "text": "These miners are enslaved in a mine shaft"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 939795.0,
      "end_time": 942753.0,
      "text": "in another part of Ghana."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 942753.0,
      "end_time": 945666.0,
      "text": "When they came out of the shaft, they were soaking wet"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 945666.0,
      "end_time": 947623.0,
      "text": "from their own sweat."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 947623.0,
      "end_time": 951589.0,
      "text": "I remember looking into their tired, bloodshot eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 951589.0,
      "end_time": 957745.0,
      "text": "for many of them had been underground for 72 hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 957745.0,
      "end_time": 961329.0,
      "text": "The shafts are up to 300 feet deep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 961329.0,
      "end_time": 964257.0,
      "text": "and they carry out heavy bags of stone"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 964257.0,
      "end_time": 967417.0,
      "text": "that later will be transported to another area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 967417.0,
      "end_time": 970061.0,
      "text": "where the stone will be pounded"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 970061.0,
      "end_time": 973389.0,
      "text": "so that they can extract the gold."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 973389.0,
      "end_time": 975053.0,
      "text": "At first glance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 975053.0,
      "end_time": 980543.0,
      "text": "the pounding site seems full of powerful men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 980543.0,
      "end_time": 984782.0,
      "text": "but when we look closer, we see some less fortunate"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 984782.0,
      "end_time": 986734.0,
      "text": "working on the fringes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 986734.0,
      "end_time": 988900.0,
      "text": "and children too."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 988900.0,
      "end_time": 998907.0,
      "text": "All of them are victim to injury, illness and violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 998907.0,
      "end_time": 1003037.0,
      "text": "In fact, it&#39;s very likely that this muscular person"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1003040.0,
      "end_time": 1007671.0,
      "text": "will end up like this one here, racked with tuberculosis"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1007670.0,
      "end_time": 1014072.0,
      "text": "and mercury poisoning in just a few years."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1014070.0,
      "end_time": 1016336.0,
      "text": "This is Manuru."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1016340.0,
      "end_time": 1018108.0,
      "text": "When his father died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1018100.0,
      "end_time": 1021327.0,
      "text": "his uncle trafficked him to work with him in the mines."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1021330.0,
      "end_time": 1025840.0,
      "text": "When his uncle died, Manuru inherited his uncle&#39;s debt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1025839.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1030636.9999999999,
      "text": "which further forced him into being enslaved in the mines."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1030640.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1032269.0000000001,
      "text": "When I met him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1032270.0,
      "end_time": 1035843.0,
      "text": "he had been working in the mines for 14 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1035839.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1038301.9999999999,
      "text": "and the leg injury that you see here"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1038300.0,
      "end_time": 1040386.0,
      "text": "is actually from a mining accident,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1040390.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1045821.0000000001,
      "text": "one so severe doctors say his leg should be amputated."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1045819.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1049347.0,
      "text": "On top of that, Manuru has tuberculosis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1049350.0,
      "end_time": 1054554.0,
      "text": "yet he&#39;s still forced to work day in and day out in that mine shaft."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1054550.0,
      "end_time": 1057823.0,
      "text": "Even still, he has a dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1057820.0,
      "end_time": 1061188.0,
      "text": "that he will become free and become educated"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1061190.0,
      "end_time": 1065285.0,
      "text": "with the help of local activists like Free the Slaves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1065290.0,
      "end_time": 1068042.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s this sort of determination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1068040.0,
      "end_time": 1072093.0,
      "text": "in the face of unimaginable odds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1072090.0,
      "end_time": 1079182.0,
      "text": "that fills me with complete awe."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1079180.0,
      "end_time": 1082408.0,
      "text": "I want to shine a light on slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1082410.0,
      "end_time": 1084751.0,
      "text": "When I was working in the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1084750.0,
      "end_time": 1087235.0,
      "text": "I brought lots of candles with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1087240.0,
      "end_time": 1089833.0,
      "text": "and with the help of my interpreter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1089830.0,
      "end_time": 1092153.0,
      "text": "I imparted to the people I was photographing"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1092150.0,
      "end_time": 1095388.0,
      "text": "that I wanted to illuminate their stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1095390.0,
      "end_time": 1097150.0,
      "text": "and their plight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1097150.0,
      "end_time": 1100845.0,
      "text": "so when it was safe for them, and safe for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1100850.0,
      "end_time": 1104386.0,
      "text": "I made these images."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1104380.0,
      "end_time": 1108811.0,
      "text": "They knew their image would be seen by you out in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1108810.0,
      "end_time": 1111327.0,
      "text": "I wanted them to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1111330.0,
      "end_time": 1115037.0,
      "text": "that we will be bearing witness to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1115040.0,
      "end_time": 1118048.0,
      "text": "and that we will do whatever we can"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1118050.0,
      "end_time": 1121943.0,
      "text": "to help make a difference in their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1121940.0,
      "end_time": 1123862.0,
      "text": "I truly believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1123860.0,
      "end_time": 1127647.0,
      "text": "if we can see one another as fellow human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1127650.0,
      "end_time": 1129700.0,
      "text": "then it becomes very difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1129700.0,
      "end_time": 1135080.0,
      "text": "to tolerate atrocities like slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1135080.0,
      "end_time": 1137321.0,
      "text": "These images are not of issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1137320.0,
      "end_time": 1141144.0,
      "text": "They are of people, real people, like you and me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1141140.0,
      "end_time": 1143533.0,
      "text": "all deserving of the same rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1143540.0,
      "end_time": 1147607.0,
      "text": "dignity and respect in their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 1147600.0,
      "end_time": 1150236.0,
      "text": "There is not a day that goes by"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 1150240.0,
      "end_time": 1152561.0,
      "text": "that I don&#39;t think of these many"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 1152560.0,
      "end_time": 1155911.0,
      "text": "beautiful, mistreated people"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 1155910.0,
      "end_time": 1162441.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had the tremendous honor of meeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 1162440.0,
      "end_time": 1165428.0,
      "text": "I hope that these images awaken a force"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 1165430.0,
      "end_time": 1168692.0,
      "text": "in those who view them, people like you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 1168690.0,
      "end_time": 1172853.0,
      "text": "and I hope that force will ignite a fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 1172850.0,
      "end_time": 1177805.0,
      "text": "and that fire will shine a light on slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 1177810.0,
      "end_time": 1180138.0,
      "text": "for without that light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 1180140.0,
      "end_time": 1185522.0,
      "text": "the beast of bondage can continue to live in the shadows."
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 1185520.0,
      "end_time": 1187833.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 1187830.0,
      "end_time": 1197830.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}